title: Whiny Whiny Rhino
description: Can Tiny Tiny Rhino have a fun day? Or will all of his whining get in the way? If you've ever been worried to try something new, then Whiny Whiny Rhino is the book for you! From creative team McBoop, comes the story of the whiny rhino with the big head and the even bigger imagination.
author: McBoop
